  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong># Questions, Doubts... Truth!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"What if robots gained free will? Would they still exist for humanity's sake?\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2030, a world where robots and humans coexist faces a chilling series of murders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The prime suspects? Robots living among us.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unearth the scattered evidence at crime scenes,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and navigate through the web of truth and deception in the robots' testimonies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/0dff1508227a62746ae50bf8511fd5fb.avif?t=1760355284\" width=614 height=346 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong># No Choices, Only Questions.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your questions are the keys to unraveling the case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All victims are linked to an experiment called \"Project Atlas.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subject X, Atlas Chip, and H.R.P.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What massive truth is hidden behind this chain of events?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/9488347a270d1e8083056904467feb5d.poster.avif?t=1760355284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/9488347a270d1e8083056904467feb5d.webm?t=1760355284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/9488347a270d1e8083056904467feb5d.mp4?t=1760355284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong># Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Experience 5 gripping episodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Engage in deep conversations with case-related robots to uncover the incident's full story and crucial clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- If the suspect robot is the culprit, trigger system overload questions to switch them to confession mode, revealing the incident's truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover hidden stories by finding all evidence and confirming the case's truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Utilize the investigation status board actively to ensure you don't miss any vital clues or decisive questions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/5a428cbcada4b01b21474d2b8557d40e.poster.avif?t=1760355284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/5a428cbcada4b01b21474d2b8557d40e.webm?t=1760355284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2492290/extras/5a428cbcada4b01b21474d2b8557d40e.mp4?t=1760355284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
